{{Quote|These Kuat starfighters have the firepower and the maneuverability Jedi pilots prize.|Jedi Starfighter 3R3 flavour text|<ref name="AOTC:TCG">{{TCG|set=Attack of the Clones|cardname=Jedi Starfighter 3R3}}</ref>}}
'''3R3''' was the designation of a [[Kuat Systems Engineering/Legends|Kuat Systems Engineering]] [[Delta-7 Aethersprite-class light interceptor/Legends|Delta-7 ''Aethersprite''-class light interceptor]] in service with the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] prior to and during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. Its [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] flew with a green-domed [[R4 astromech droid/Legends|R4-series agromech droid]].

